{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fcd22afad4","title":"中共四川省委办公厅关于肿病情况反映","origin":"四川省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"33229b1bf7","index":0,"year":1960,"month":4,"day":29,"articleId":"fcd22afad4"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"25a2d7d4b4","type":"title","text":"中共四川省委办公厅关于肿病情况反映","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fcd22afad4"},{"id":"13e2436bf4","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）据省除害灭病办公室反映，今春以来全省有140个县（市）发生肿病（注：全省共有178个县、市）。病人中农村较多，城市、厂矿、工地和学校也有发生。全省从元月分发病以来，最高时发病率达1.41％，约110万人，现在尚有病人1,074,730人。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fcd22afad4"},{"id":"6875e14e48","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）病人达2万以上者有以下12个专区","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fcd22afad4"},{"id":"4978bebf84","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fcd22afad4"},{"id":"3a327579ad","type":"paragraph","text":"   县名 除害灭病办公室4月上旬 掌握数字 地委及检查团材料   得病人数 占总人数％ 得病人数 占总人数％   绵阳专区 124,720 1.3％ - -   江津专区 119,410 2.18％ - -   涪陵专区 104,320 2.34％ 112,987 2.53％   内江专区 96,050 1.52％ - -   乐山专区 83,290 1.9％ 128,068 2.92％   万县专区 70,440 1.25％ - -   泸州专区 67,760 1.51％ - -   温江专区 59,910 1.19％ - -   达县专区 57,530 0.89％ - -   雅安专区 50,650 5.33％ 50,480 5.31％   宜宾专区 43,980 1.61％ - -   南充专区 42,150 0.58％ - -   ","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fcd22afad4"},{"id":"530614a37f","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）发病严重的有以下35个县","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fcd22afad4"},{"id":"5b5f05d45d","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"fcd22afad4"},{"id":"63af245f85","type":"paragraph","text":"   县名 除害灭病办公室4月上旬 掌握数字 地县委及检查团反映的材料   病人数 占全县人数％ 病人数 占全县人数％   眉山县 14,950 1.85％ 34,645 4.28％   井研 12,950 4.4